%% Data Flow Diagram: Model Metadata Collection
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant CI as Konflux/CI Pipeline
    participant Extractor as model-extractor<br/>(Go CLI)
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Reg as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>(output/ & data/)
    participant Build as Container Build<br/>(Dockerfile.konflux)
    participant Quay as quay.io Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Consumer as Model Registry /<br/>Dashboard Pod

    Note over CI,Consumer: Flow 1: Model Metadata Extraction Pipeline (Build-Time)

    CI->>Extractor: Execute model-extractor
    Extractor->>HF: GET /api/collections (search)<br/>No Auth
    HF-->>Extractor: Collection list (RedHatAI validated models)
    Extractor->>HF: GET /api/users/RedHatAI/collections<br/>No Auth
    HF-->>Extractor: User collections
    Extractor->>HF: GET /api/collections/{slug}<br/>No Auth
    HF-->>Extractor: Collection model list

    loop For each model in collection
        Extractor->>Reg: GET /v2/{repo}/{image}/manifests/{tag}<br/>Auth: Docker config.json
        Reg-->>Extractor: OCI manifest (annotations, timestamps)
        Extractor->>Reg: Fetch image layers<br/>(modelcard annotation)<br/>Auth: Docker config.json
        Reg-->>Extractor: Model card content (markdown)
        Extractor->>Extractor: Parse YAML frontmatter<br/>& extract metadata
        Extractor->>HF: GET /api/models/{model}<br/>No Auth
        HF-->>Extractor: Model details (license, tags, downloads)
        Extractor->>HF: GET /{model}/raw/main/README.md<br/>No Auth
        HF-->>Extractor: README content (provider extraction)
        Extractor->>Extractor: Enrich metadata<br/>(similarity matching, tag parsing)
    end

    Extractor->>FS: Write models-catalog.yaml
    Extractor->>FS: Write validated-models-catalog.yaml

    Note over CI,Consumer: Flow 2: Container Image Build and Distribution

    CI->>Build: Trigger container build
    Build->>Build: COPY data/*.yaml /app/data/
    Build->>Build: COPY sample-data/ /app/benchmarks/
    Build->>Build: Set USER 1001 (catalog)
    CI->>Quay: Push odh-model-metadata-collection<br/>Auth: QUAY_USERNAME/QUAY_PASSWORD
    Quay-->>CI: Image pushed successfully

    Note over CI,Consumer: Flow 3: Runtime Data Consumption

    Consumer->>Consumer: Mount data container volume
    Consumer->>Consumer: Read /app/data/models-catalog.yaml
    Consumer->>Consumer: Read /app/data/validated-models-catalog.yaml
